    A company has decided to use 1000 thousand yuan of a new product development fund to invest in the development of three new products: A, B, and C. Forecasted return on investment (ROI) for each product is: Product A: 5%, Product B: 7%, Product C: 10%, Due to associated risks, the company has defined the following priority constraints: 1.At least 300 thousand yuan must be invested in Product A. 2.To diversify investment risk, no single product may receive more than 35% of the total fund. 3.At least 10% of the fund (i.e., 1 million yuan) must be reserved for emergency use.4.The objective is to maximize total profit from the investment. 
Please formulate a model to maximize the total investment profit(in thousand yuan).

-------------
【Python Gurobi 代码】:
 ```python
from gurobipy import Model, GRB

# Create model
model = Model("Investment_Optimization")

# Total fund (in thousand yuan)
total_fund = 1000

# Decision variables (investment amounts in thousand yuan)
A = model.addVar(lb=0, name="Product_A")
B = model.addVar(lb=0, name="Product_B")
C = model.addVar(lb=0, name="Product_C")
R = model.addVar(lb=0, name="Reserve_Fund")

# Objective function: Maximize total profit (in thousand yuan)
model.setObjective(0.05 * A + 0.07 * B + 0.10 * C, GRB.MAXIMIZE)

# Constraints

# 1. At least 300 thousand yuan invested in Product A
model.addConstr(A >= 300, name="Min_Investment_A")

# 2. No single product receives more than 35% of total fund
model.addConstr(A <= 0.35 * total_fund, name="Max_Investment_A")
model.addConstr(B <= 0.35 * total_fund, name="Max_Investment_B")
model.addConstr(C <= 0.35 * total_fund, name="Max_Investment_C")

# 3. At least 10% of total fund reserved for emergency use
model.addConstr(R >= 0.10 * total_fund, name="Min_Reserve")

# 4. Total allocation equals total fund
model.addConstr(A + B + C + R == total_fund, name="Total_Fund_Constraint")

# Optimize model
model.optimize()

# Output results
if model.status == GRB.OPTIMAL:
    print(f"Optimal Investment in Product A: {A.x:.2f} thousand yuan")
    print(f"Optimal Investment in Product B: {B.x:.2f} thousand yuan")
    print(f"Optimal Investment in Product C: {C.x:.2f} thousand yuan")
    print(f"Reserve Fund: {R.x:.2f} thousand yuan")
    print(f"Maximum Total Profit: {model.objVal:.2f} thousand yuan")
