  Table 7-4  
  million yuan  


  <html><body><table><tr><td rowspan="2">m_{ij} （Plan）</td><td colspan="2">Factory i=1</td><td colspan="2">Factory i=2</td><td colspan="2">Factory i=3</td></tr><tr><td>Investment</td><td>Return</td><td>Investment</td><td>Return</td><td>Investment</td><td>Return</td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>5</td><td>2</td><td>8</td><td>1</td><td>3</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>6</td><td>3</td><td>9</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>4</td><td>12</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr></table></body></html>

  (Note: “–” indicates that the plan is not available for that factory)  

